# 🛠️ E-commerce Website Backend

Welcome to the **backend** of the 🛍️ E-commerce Website – built with **Node.js** and **Express.js**, this service powers all your store’s server-side logic, including authentication, product & order management.

![Node Animation](https://media.giphy.com/media/coxQHKASG60HrHtvkt/giphy.gif)

---

## 🔐 Features

- 👤 **User Authentication** – Signup, login, and secure access using **JWT**
- 📦 **Product Management** – Add, update, delete, and list products
- 🧾 **Order Management** – Create and view customer orders
- 🧠 **MongoDB** – Stores user, product, and order data
- 🔐 **Security** – Password encryption, validation, and secure headers

---

## 💻 Technologies Used

| Tech         | Purpose                             |
|--------------|--------------------------------------|
| 🟩 Node.js    | JavaScript runtime environment       |
| 🚂 Express.js | Lightweight server & routing         |
| 🍃 MongoDB    | NoSQL document database              |
| 🔐 JWT        | Token-based authentication           |
| 📦 Mongoose   | MongoDB object modeling              |
| 🧂 Bcrypt     | Password hashing & salting           |

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

```bash
# 🔁 Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/veerendra4401/Ecommerce-Website.git

# 📂 Navigate to the backend folder
cd Ecommerce-Website/backend

# 📦 Install dependencies
npm install

# ⚙️ Create .env file and add:
# MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
# JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key

# 🚀 Start the server
npm start
